{
  "$schema": "https://opencode.ai/config.json",
  // ==================================================
  // Open Questions & Decisions
  // ==================================================
  //
  // ## Mental model to select which agent for the task :
  // Main = models I use most
  // Reviewers = second opinions
  // Small/local = lightweight options
  // Parked = documented but not currently in rotation
  //
  // Main
  // - build / plan -> Kimi 2.5 Fireworks
  // - @gpt         -> GPT
  //
  // Reviewers
  // - @grok      -> Grok 4.20
  // - @gemini-or -> Gemini 3.1 Pro via OpenRouter
  // - @glm       -> GLM 5 via Zen
  //
  // Parked
  // - @kimi25 -> Kimi 2.5 via Zen
  // - @opus   -> Opus
  // - @glm47  -> GLM 4.7
  // - @qwen   -> Qwen (via LM Studio)
  //
  // ## Defaults
  // Default agent = build = Kimi 2.5 Turbo via Fireworks
  // Why: fast, cheap, good daily tradeoff
  // Note: no active Kimi variants yet, so Ctrl+T does nothing for now.
  //
  // Fallback top-level model = GLM 5 via Zen
  // small_model = Gemini Flash via OpenRouter
  //
  // ## GPT routing
  // Use direct OpenAI Plus plan for GPT.
  // Do not route GPT through OpenRouter, Zen, or another proxy.
  // Keep GPT as the medium default.
  // Use separate agents for higher effort levels.
  //
  // ## Gemini routing
  // Use OpenRouter for Gemini.
  // Reason: Gemini via Zen/Xen is not working reliably, and OpenRouter is the current working path. [[2026-03-14]]
  // Reasoning via thinking levels (minimal, low, medium, high)
  //
  // Active Gemini reviewers
  // - @flash-or  -> Gemini 3 Flash via OpenRouter
  // - @gemini-or -> Gemini 3.1 Pro via OpenRouter
  //
  // ## Grok routing
  // Use OpenRouter for Grok. Reason: the latest Grok is not available on Zen. [[2026-03-14]]
  //
  // ## GLM routing
  // Keep direct ZAI access for GLM 4.7.
  // Use Zen for GLM 5. Reason: direct ZAI does not give me GLM 5 [[2026-03-14]]
  //
  // ## Local model usage
  // Keep one local LM Studio model.
  // Qwen is my local small-task option.
  //
  // ## Claude usage
  // Keep Opus documented, but parked for now. Reason: I do not currently have an Anthropic plan [[2026-03-14]]
  //
  // ==================================================
